    <title>Register | Secure Vault</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400">üîê Secure Vault</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mt-2">Create an account to start securing your secrets.</p>
